twitter.com/phantompainss&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;@phantompainss&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pHUDj7距离更轻薄的 PlayStation 5 发布仅几周时间，一位用户似乎已经拿到了更新后的游戏机。在发布到 X（以前称为 Twitter）的一系列图片中，&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/phantompainss/status/1719423461049643090?s=20&quot;>;用户 @phantompainss&lt;/a>; 展示了更新后的控制台堆栈的方式与更粗的对应物相比。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;c5iLsQ&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911388/new-ps5-model-slim-size-比较&quot;>;新的 PS5&lt;/a>; 看起来与原来的游戏机相比，它的占地面积会稍微小一些。它不仅具有比标准 PS5 更纤薄的外形，而且还短了几英寸。尽管设计更薄，但该设备的背面似乎保留了与其前身相同的端口，包括一个 HDMI 端口、两个 USB 端口、一个电源连接器和一个以太网端口。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image &quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/phantompainss/status/1719423461049643090?s=20&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;@phantompainss&lt;/a>;&lt; /cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;57xOXQ&quot;>;图像也出现...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/ 23941001/ps5-slim-original-sony-playstation-images&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23941001/ps5-slim-original-sony-playstation-images" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23941001/ps5-slim-original-sony-playstation-images</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-31T17:51:19-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-31T17:51:19-04:00</updated><title> Match 退出 Google Play 反垄断对决</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/CHFdEjYCujmGyx4kIqKi9AwHMmQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72815211/STK093_Google_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Nm2PBg&quot;>;Match Group 和 Google 周二宣布就 Match 对该公司的诉讼达成和解。最后一刻的决定使得谷歌计划在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/7/23907649/epic-”中与《堡垒之夜》发行商 Epic Games 单独对抗v-google-antitrust-lawsuit-andy-rubin-sundar-pichai&quot;>;反垄断审判&lt;/a>;将于下周开始，Epic 指控 Google Play 的付款政策具有反竞争性。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wenRqN &quot;>;Match 于 2022 年 5 月&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/5/9/23064305/match-group-suing-google-over-in-app- payment-policy&quot;>;起诉 Google &lt;/a>;，指控该公司通过 Google Play“非法垄断应用程序分发市场”，并对其从市场交易中收取的费用征收“敲诈性税”。其主张与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/8/19/22632804/epic-google-lawsuit-unredacted-complaint-antitrust&quot;>;Epic 的现有投诉&lt;/a>;相吻合：以及州总检察长联盟。 Google 和各州宣布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.courthousenews.com/states-google-reach-tentative-deal-to-settle-google-play-monopoly-suit/&quot;>;他们自己的和解&lt;/a >; 九月。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3hdxvL&quot;>;根据最新的条款...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10 /31/23941071/google-play-match-group-antitrust-settlement-epic-games&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23941071/google-play-match-group-antitrust-settlement-epic-games" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23941071/google-play-match-group-antitrust-settlement-epic-games</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-31T17:21:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-31T17:21:11-04:00</updated><title> M2 与 M3：新款 MacBook Pro 的比较</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;某人在水边的窗户旁使用 MacBook Pro 的图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fqvlpYZE9KdMO-22cUJo0_LmocY=/188x0:2213x1350/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72815167/Apple_MacBook_Pro_lifestyle_screen.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Wd9mWW&quot;>;除了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/30/23938798/ apple-m3-imac-price-specs-release-date-event&quot;>;新款 iMac&lt;/a>;，Apple 宣布推出新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/30/23939089 /apple-m3-macbook-pro-touch-bar-specs-features-price-release-date&quot;>;14 英寸和 1